rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0001
rows.name:
We at Kurolo are discussing how to buy
the shop's products more cheaply, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0002
rows.name:
We're thinking tirelessly for the poor people
living in Torika Alley, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The current method is to stimulate
the economy, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If everyone buys a lot, then demand will
increase, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Then, mass production will begin, mo.
And with mass production, the unit price will
drop, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Shopping develops the country, and as the
country develops, products become cheaper!
That's how it works, mo!
